Description: oidentd is an ident (rfc1413 compliant) daemon
DescDetail: <<
oidentd has a flexible mechanism for specifying ident responses.  Users can
be granted permission to specify their own ident responses.  Responses can be
specified according to host and port pairs.

WARNING
There is no daemonic script and no default configuration supplied, thus
read the man pages carefully on how to setup your own environment.
<<
